rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Let's take a nice walk over to the hall
where the emergency summit's being
held. Clear our heads a little.

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Someone's gotta escort Meleph
over there, right?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0006
rows.name:
I think I would be perfectly capable
of finding my own way...

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0007
rows.name:
And Hikari's meant to be attending
too, right?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0009
rows.name: See? We might as well all head over.

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0010
rows.name:
I guess you're right...
Let's go, then.
